JOHANNESBURG – eNCA's Sally Burdett is returning to the screen to anchor the 8 pm bulletin. Burdett will make her appearance on Monday. READ: New team for eNCA 'News Night' “I am delighted to be back on e.tv, on a bulletin I have always loved,” says Burdett. “The news at 8 pm will be to-the-point and hard-hitting, continuing a fearless tradition of seeking the truth”. She is also the head of the anchor team at eNCA. eNCA